<div class="container top">
	<div class="row" id="blogSearchContainer">
        <div class="six columns" id="blogSearchBlurbContainer">
				A little research can go a long way in helping you make the most of your volunteer experience.  Use this section to find websites, articles, and blog posts on cool, useful stuff.

		</div>
		<div class="six columns" id="blogSearchFieldContainer">
			<form accept-charset="UTF-8" action="/blog_posts/blog_search" method="get"><input name="utf8" type="hidden" value="&#x2713;" />
				<div class="blogSearchMagGlassContainer">
					<input id="searchbutton" value="search" type="image" src="https://s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/volunteervoice/images/magGlassSmaller.png" id="blogSearchMagGlassButton" alt="Search Button" onmousedown="this.className = 'shadowed'" onmouseup="this.className='nothing'">
				</div>
				<input id="searchfield" name="search" type="text" class="blogSearchField" />
			</form>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row" id="blogColumnsContainer">
		<div class="four columns" id="practical_table">
			<div align="center">
				<image class="blogTitleImage" src="https://s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/volunteervoice/images/practical.png"><br />
			</div>

			<div align="center" class="leftColumnSubTitleContainer"><p class="leftColumnSubTitleInnerContainer"><span class="leftColumnSubTitleRed">RESEARCH </span> WHERE YOU'RE GOING</p></div><br />
			<div class="articleList">
<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/index.html" target="_blank">The CIA World Factbook</a>
<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">An excellent, simple, and straight-forward website with a lot of potent info on all of the worldâ€™s countries. Learn! </p><br /><br />
</div>

<div align="center"><p class="leftColumnSubTitleInnerContainer">LEARN THE <span class="leftColumnSubTitleRed">LANGUAGE </span></p></div><br />
<div class="articleList">
<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "http://www.livemocha.com" target="_blank">LiveMocha --Free Language Courses.</a>
<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">So many languages here. You can also chat with native speakers through this site for practice. Excellent for beginners.</p><br />
<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "http://www.busuu.com/enc/" target="_blank">Busuu --Free Language Courses.</a>
<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">More free online courses. Some stuff you must pay for.  Different style curriculum that may/may not suit you better.</p><br />
<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "http://www.openculture.com/freelanguagelessons" target="_blank">Open Culture --Free Language Course Directory.</a>
<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">More free online courses. Some stuff you must pay for.  Different style curriculum that may/may not suit you better.</p><br /><br />

</div>



<div align="center"><p class="leftColumnSubTitleInnerContainer">GET A <span class="leftColumnSubTitleRed">VISA </span></p></div><br />
<div class="articleList">
<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "http://www.delta.com/planning_reservations/plan_flight/international_travel_information/visa_passport_information/index.jsp" target="_blank">Delta Visa Search Engine</a>

<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">Enter your country of citizenship and destination country to find out visa requirements. Good idea.</p><br />
<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "http://www.embassyworld.com/embassy/directory.htm" target="_blank">Embassy World</a>
<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">All visas must go through an embassy or two.  You can find whichever ones you need here.</p><br /><br />
</div>


<div align="center"><p class="leftColumnSubTitleInnerContainer">HEALTH AND <span class="leftColumnSubTitleRed">SAFETY </span></p></div><br />
<div class="articleList">
<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/travel/destinations/list.htm" target="_blank">Center for Disease Control and Prevention</a>
<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">An easy to use map list of all the worlds countries, and all of the immunizations, pills, and precautions that you need to take before you get there.</p><br />
<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "http://www.travelinsurancereview.net/" target="_blank">Travel Insurance Review</a>
<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">Boring but important.  This site can help you compare travel insurance plans before committing to one.</p><br /><br />
</div>



<div align="center"><p class="leftColumnSubTitleInnerContainer"> <span class="leftColumnSubTitleRed">FLIGHT  </span> &nbsp; INFO</p></div><br />
<div class="articleList">
<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "http://www.flyforgood.com" target="_blank">Fly For Good</a>
<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">International volunteers can get discounted plane tickets here.</p><br />
<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "http://www.statravel.com" target="_blank">STA Travel</a>

<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">Just being a student can also get you discounted airfare for you trip, so check this site out if you apply.</p><br /><br />
</div>


<div align="center"><p class="leftColumnSubTitleInnerContainer"><span class="leftColumnSubTitleRed">FUNDING </span> YOUR TRIP</p></div><br />
<div class="articleList">
<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "http://www.gofundme.com" target="_blank">GoFundMe</a>
<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">A free online fundraising platform (they take a small % of of what you raise) where you can post a profile for your trip.</p><br />


<a class="leftColumnTitleOfSource" href= "http://www.microgiving.com" target="_blank">Microgiving</a>
<p class="leftColumnArticleBody">Another online platform.  Post a profile for your cause and send out the link like crazy.</p><br /><br />
</div>
</div>




<div class="four columns" id="interesting_table">
	<div align="center">
<image class="blogTitleImage" src="https://s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/volunteervoice/images/interesting.png"><br /></div>
	<div id="divarticles">
	<% @interesting.each do |f| %>
	<%= render :partial => "interesting", :locals => {:f => f}%>
	<% end %>
	</div>
	<div id="article_pager"></div>

</div>


<% @our_blog = @our_blog.sort_by(&:created_at).reverse%>
<div class="four columns" id="our_blog_table">
	<div align="center" class="ourBlogTitleContainer">
<a href="/blog_posts" class="ourBlogImageLink"><image class="ourBlogImage blogTitleImage" src="https://s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/volunteervoice/images/ourBlog.png" href="/blog_posts"></a><br /></div>
	<div id="divOurBlog">
	<% @our_blog.each do |f| %>
	<%= render :partial => "our_blog", :locals => {:f => f}%>
	<% end %>
	</div>
	<div id="our_pager"></div>
</div>
</div>


<script type="text/javascript">
$(document).ready(function() {
	//Initialize the "article posts" smartpaginator pagination on 'divarticles'
		//article_pager will be contain "1-1 of 4", ">", etc.
	$('#article_pager').smartpaginator({ totalrecords: <%=@interesting.count%>, recordsperpage: 4, datacontainer: 'divarticles', dataelement: 'table', initval: 0, next: 'Next', prev: 'Prev', first: 'First', last: 'Last', theme: 'black' });

	//Initialize the "our blog posts" smartpaginator pagination on 'divOurBlog'
		//our_pager will be contain "1-1 of 4", ">", etc.
    $('#our_pager').smartpaginator({ totalrecords: <%=@our_blog.count%>, recordsperpage: 5, datacontainer: 'divOurBlog', dataelement: 'table', initval: 0, next: 'Next', prev: 'Prev', first: 'First', last: 'Last', theme: 'black' });



//Opera does not center blog posts within columns. This code is to center them in opera
	if ($.browser.opera) {
		$(".interesting_blog_post").css("marginLeft", "-13px");
		$(".our_blog_post").css("marginLeft", "-13px");
	}
	
});
</script>
